* 1968: &quot;It Doesn&#x27;t Matter How I Say It (It&#x27;s What I Say That Matters)&quot; b/w &quot;Goin&#x27; Out of My Head&quot; (ABC Records #45-11074A/B)
* 1968: &quot;Love Ain&#x27;t Love&quot; b/w &quot;Forever Faithful&quot; (ABC Records #45-11144A/B)

